data.description: This beautiful townhouse shows like a brand new home! Move right on in and make this gorgeous 3 bed, 2.5 bath model yours! Enjoy open concept living at its finest in the expansive living/dining/kitchen grand-room with hardwood-like flooring. The well-appointed kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry and large center island perfect for entertaining! You’ll f ind extra high ceilings in the living space downstairs and a convenient laundry room with a tankless water heater on the upper level. Relax in the spacious, sunlit primary bedroom, showcasing two generous closets, one a walk-in, and gorgeous en-suite with a two sink vanity and large shower enclosure. The large finished garage has a bonus space for storage, a workshop, or an exercise area. Two cars can easily park side by side in the garage and there might even be room for a third vehicle to be parked in tandem... The Villages at Arnold is a newer townhome neighborhood with views of distant hills, thoughtfully landscaped grounds and play area! Convenient access to BART, freeways and shopping.
